text: La Encantada may refer to: ==Places== *La Encantada (shopping center), a shopping center in Tucson, Arizona, United States *La Encantada, Colón, a corregimiento in Panama ==Other uses== *Diwata (देवता; encantada), a type of spirit in Philippine mythology ==See also== *Encantado (disambiguation) *Encantador (disambiguation) *La Encantadora, DC Comics cosmic entity supervillain *El Encantador, Colombian telenovela
title: La Encantada
